Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.55,0:02:15.74,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Strict control of reason and reality
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.76,0:02:20.17,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Cut myself and scream for their insanity
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:24.49,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Wake up into this nightmare that will never end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.53,0:02:29.25,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}The main attraction of this twisted master plan
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.02,0:02:46.18,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I will be your deadman
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.27,0:02:50.62,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}With nothing but this blood on my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:55.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stuck in your Wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.13,0:02:59.49,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I wanna make you bleed just like me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:03.98,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}So make me your deadman
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:08.28,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}With only poison in my veins
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:12.65,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stuck in your Wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:14.94,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Stuck in a battle I have to make
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:17.72,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I'm gonna make you bleed like me


Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:25.03,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(550,505)\pos(916,560)}#11   绝望的GIG
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再给我巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 「Wretched Egg」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你从昨天开始就只顾着吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.20,0:03:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Wretch Dog」?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是「Wretched Egg」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白 我叫做白!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白 你那么受伤吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.96,0:03:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为被朋友打了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸还很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛? 你?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白我啊 可是「Aceman」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从成为了「Aceman」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就再也感觉不到痛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:55.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白都是「Aceman」了 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.54,0:04:01.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会被丸太讨厌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么曲奇不好吃了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:08.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么吃了那么多 这里却仍填不满呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是个臭丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是个弱茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会让我这么痛?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有必要去感受痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和从前一样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易救了他 结果却适得其反了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怜啊 弱小的人往往都很狡猾没责任感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,归咎于别人 包庇自己伤害他人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白很重视那么弱的家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不重视 我讨厌丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 都是丸太不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.06,0:04:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就去扁他一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.37,0:04:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 这居然含酒精
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全变成点心大会了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 不 鄙人也要吃些点心了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃好多甜甜的「罪之枝」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将放弃解救凪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然战力不足
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只能打游击战 各自找路线想办法逃出升天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 六路供出的路线也不见得安全啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪都没有安全路线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果遇到守墓者那帮家伙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:32.62,Float,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(598,653)}Undertaker
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可就 那啥了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来他还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就靠现有的这些人搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉他的是假时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得那样更好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会恨你吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为我信错了人 才害他受了那么多的罪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他早就该恨我了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还很年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怀揣各自的伤痕和自由
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要战斗到底
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.24,0:06:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了斩断这个枷锁
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 你还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙的存活率 最多只有32%吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.43,0:06:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还是没遇到守墓者的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:25.22,Float,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(708,653)}Undertaker
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要成功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你不会是打算一个人潜入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:32.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根本不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.96,0:06:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对要做给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使最后自己死掉?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残酷的计算啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是从妻子那里拿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想随身带着孩子的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男孩? 女孩?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.57,0:06:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为有着这个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使身处在这不合理的DW地下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能够满怀希望地活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天雨会停 天会蓝 彩虹也一定会出现
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这样认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个傻瓜父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.93,0:07:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 很像你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样你就死了12次了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓄力时间太长 炮弹太弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轨道太容易看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大的问题是你太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发不出超音速的炮弹来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.60,0:07:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音速?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用身体记住如何操纵血
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.40,0:07:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把血当成自己的手和脚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 但是我该怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太 现在有Candy吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.22,0:08:08.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都带在身上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你做什么啊 千地先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.74,0:08:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那里将这颗Candy打落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要突破我的防守
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的丸太炮 如果慢过我的虚空一闪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:28.67,Float,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(886,653)}Invisible Black
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么恭喜 你就被判死刑了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只有提高速度了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.14,0:08:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 来吧 五十岚丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不够不够
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓄力还得更快些!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看见白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.13,0:09:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「仿声鸟」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说要去打五十岚丸太 之后就冲了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:17.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白的朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了 「乌鸦」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过得怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这阵子干什么去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 稍微死了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没想和你打
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:43.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你这么爱我 鄙人倒是很高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.61,0:09:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前是这种性格吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.34,0:09:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你刚才在作甚!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「仿声鸟」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:58.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为最强「Deadman」的战斗狂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:02.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也发生了很多事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是最弱的「Deadman」呦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一点血 就送给我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也舔舔你怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「啄木鸟」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙现在还在特训中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一滴血也不能浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要找的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎没来他这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去别处看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 鄙人是「仿声鸟」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:42.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咲神斗都
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.91,0:10:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我斗都吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照了 「啄木鸟」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 白呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残存的苍蝇们似乎还在蠢蠢欲动呢 弦角
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好用来打发时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.27,0:11:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,创办人兼新所长可是很忙的呦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还得开始制作新的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点让游戏结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.32,0:11:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 新所长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要的东西也到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.88,0:11:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么声音?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 红花绽开的声音而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦角段长到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那以后 他就一直闭门不出了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.58,0:12:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 佐藤还没出来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就要走一步算一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.48,0:12:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我 凪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是自由之锁么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.17,Float,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,653)}Scar Chain
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走错了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.97,0:12:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能来这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是弄坏我吉他的白毛女么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.86,0:12:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 她好像迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.39,0:12:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻就送她回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一只苍蝇么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一开口我就知道了 「斗鸡」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快到时间了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一小时 再练一会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:26.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 在这儿倒下就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.41,0:13:27.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必死无疑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千地先生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你参加了他们的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只会拖后腿 必然第一个挂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样都得白死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,省省吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:49.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 炮弹太小了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:55.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血量不够
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 刚才那一发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.23,0:14:15.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贫血了么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fucking 自由之锁的兔崽子们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.61,0:14:25.28,Float,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(604,653)}Scar Chain
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.11,0:14:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还没被虐够么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.94,0:14:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃才是大彻大悟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 我就不布道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌抓人游戏跟躲猫猫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我就立马弄死这几个人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是过来受死 还是逃着等死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就让你们自己选个死法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:54.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.60,0:14:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把凪和我的希望带出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:14:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.02,0:15:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是刚才那一发 五十岚丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这发丸太炮 「利落」地搞定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子那家伙 竟然一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:38.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们 应该做的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.59,0:15:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.91,0:15:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.51,0:15:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 在哪儿 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子小姐他们丢下我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.94,0:16:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是觉得我渣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.58,0:16:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 到此结束 你放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的超音速 就是个样子的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.91,0:16:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水名月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守墓者的老巢在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:36.29,Float,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(511,653)}Undertaker
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 连敌人在哪都不知道就一个劲瞎跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惩罚游戏欠你的 我可还了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水名月 你也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对「猫头鹰」他们的越狱游戏没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.72,0:16:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且我还有一个不是「Deadman」 却经常受伤的蠢哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 和你不一样 我可不是被冤枉的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.73,0:17:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我一定会出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.87,0:17:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.40,0:17:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐子 白 我这就来救你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 人家才没想要丸太来救呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.25,0:17:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禽兽们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:17:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 这群家伙可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 「罪之枝」怎么可能会有效
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.04,0:18:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血量要少 要尖锐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.60,0:18:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.14,0:18:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白 你没事 吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.03,0:18:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.56,0:18:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丸太!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然忘了自己的目的就来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.53,0:18:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是个孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的是… 让大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:18:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一个小鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有点不够爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说 那群家伙也很认真了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不过是匹烈马
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就开始上演绝望的GIG吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:41.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:43.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:46.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请 别靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在还很理智
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:01.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么啊 和大家一起出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你孩子还等着你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.48,0:20:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.06,0:20:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面不是什么都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老婆还怀孕的时候 就被弦角切开肚子死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子怎么可能还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我好恨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.25,0:20:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确这对你很不够意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.78,0:20:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把两个「Deadman」之间的宝贵孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.99,0:20:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄成这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.33,0:21:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经恢复正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.64,0:21:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我恨活人恨到咬牙切齿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我老婆 我孩子就非死不可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我… 和大家都还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:30.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来都已经绝望了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.11,0:21:38.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.77,0:21:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 是这么的脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.56,0:22:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为我理想中的修罗吧 「猫头鹰」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灭绝天下 普度众生

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.04,0:24:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在真正的绝望面前
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.00,0:24:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至无法去痛彻自己的无力
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.09,0:24:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.88,0:24:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让你无暇挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.26,0:24:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果认为这就是救济
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.36,0:24:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就请你闭上双眼

